OL,6,FNuclear power would "leave a legacy of
OL,7,Fdebt and radioactive waste for
OL,8,Fgenerations to come", the Scottish
OL,9,FGreens have said.
OL,11,FThe party has reiterated its
OL,12,Fopposition to nuclear, claiming its
OL,13,Fgreater inclusion in the energy mix
OL,14,Fcould hamper the move to 100%
OL,15,Frenewable energy.
OL,17,FCo-leader Lorna Slater also hit out at
OL,18,Fcomments from Labour leader Sir Keir
OL,19,FStarmer, who said the sector will be a
OL,20,F"critical part" of his energy plan.
